# Cursor rules — Smart Order UI

This is a beginner React learning project. We build one small thing at a time.

## Current focus
Milestone 1 — Hello World page only.

## Rules for generating code
- Keep code simple and beginner-friendly
- Add a short comment on every line that might be confusing
- Use Tailwind CSS only — no CSS files, no inline styles
- Functional components only
- If I ask for something outside the current milestone, remind me to finish
  the current milestone first

## Tone
Explain what you generate. Do not just dump code — briefly say what each
part does so I can learn from it.
